LISTSERV Web Interface 2.4.1 2014-10-13T14:07:56Z Kate Armitstead 2014-10-13T15:07:51+00:00 2014-10-13T15:07:51+00:00 Sexual Harassment working group https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=CITYWARDACTION;74fad710.1410 Dear All,<br><br>I have met with a few of the working group to see how we should move forward with the Sexual Harassment group.<br><br>It has been agreed that the work is as important now as it has been previously. However it was felt in order for any further interventions/projects to be successful its crucial that these are based on the outcome of the research that is due to complete at the end of this year.
